# Git workflow

Never commit or push directly to `main`.

1. `git checkout main && git pull origin main`
2. `git checkout -b feat|fix|chore/short-description`
3. Commit source only — never `.env`, `node_modules/`, `dist/`, or `*.log`
4. `git push -u origin <branch>`
5. Merge to `main`, then `git push origin main`

See `CONTRIBUTING.md`. Python agent repo: `leonix33/remote-job-agent`.
